{"tid":1035251,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"尋找阿Lam的那些年[粵]","createTime":"2019-02-24T13:33:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-25T03:15:18.000Z","uid":38456,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"4116a20d666b264a379024d84e3de418c13b1d00","tid":1035251,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:33:37.000Z","msg":"尋找阿Lam的那些年[粵]     <br />\n<br />\n「阿Lam」林子祥歌藝超卓，作品大膽創新，融合中、西文化的風格從何而來？他偕同弟弟林子輝、好友鄭丹瑞重返英國倫敦，回味昔日留學歲月。阿Lam深受當地濃厚音樂氣氛影響，還曾自組民歌組合。阿Lam和兒子林德信大玩「快問快答」，盛讚德信廣東話有進步，又提到兒子從小喜歡被人「攬攬錫錫」。德信則以貓咪形容爸爸，有何原因？阿Lam當年為後進張敬軒寫歌，結下音樂緣分。兩位「靚聲之人」即席Jam歌，樂迷有福了！"},{"pid":"b7a98064ba6b138fc583ccdcfe5af3300932b033","tid":1035251,"uid":35296,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9f2db6a04fab66680c8244f9019ba14ec4f256","tid":1035251,"uid":186189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:42:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2d62956dd6fdcd1a5549ac31087f8e4d6f5eb09","tid":1035251,"uid":37902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:43:27.000Z","msg":"好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"906981d1df4311cb15f9b91bbd8fd926dbf8d394","tid":1035251,"uid":19847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:44:44.000Z","msg":"3 0624700 3 0624770<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ac6dc2ed8eda341fd93ee1b35d36bcc8ee9920","tid":1035251,"uid":63694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019